Eurovision Song Contest supervisor Svante Stockselius said that Denmark's previous experience of hosting Eurovision events (the 2001 Contest and the first Junior Eurovision Song Contest) were influential in the Union's choice.
Further information: Voting at the Eurovision Song ContestBoth juries and televoting were used at Congratulations; both having an equal influence over the vote.
The voting was conducted in private, and the results were not announced until after the show.
